CppcheckWrapper
---------------

Internal CMake script wrapper for Cppcheck command execution.

This module provides a placeholder wrapper for future enhancements to Cppcheck
command building and execution. Currently, the Cppcheck.cmake module handles
all command building directly.

This file is included for consistency with the ClangTidyWrapper pattern.

